Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.94,0:22:25.54,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}寄り添う　二人の物語
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.54,0:22:31.11,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}色を付け道になり　交ざり合う
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.82,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}満ち足り　欠けたり
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.82,0:22:36.98,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}繰り返しながら
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.98,0:22:40.82,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}抱え込んだ昨日さえ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.60,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛してゆこう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.62,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}重なる　メロディーが
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.62,0:22:47.86,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}明日も　ずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.58,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}続きますように
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.58,0:22:56.80,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}願い込めた空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.60,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}君の声が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.52,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}聞こえるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.39,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}この歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:09.15,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.32,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どんな時でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.53,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}二人で　乘り越えてゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:18.30,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こう譲れない絆を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:25.41,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}かけがえのない　君だから
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.79,0:23:31.21,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Only for you
